reviewText: Fans of independent female pro wrestling will enjoy the views and insights of up and coming star Mia Yim in this solid shoot interview. Mia has been active for several years now, working her way up to the top of the card. Fans of Mia know how far she's come in the ring thanks to determination and hard work. And male fans know that the sexiest woman in the business doesn't work for WWE or TNA-at least not yet. Mia Yim is as hot as she is talented.
